    "content": "<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"80px\",\"bottom\":\"80px\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"#111\",\"className\":\"op-testimonials\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull op-testimonials has-background\" style=\"background-color:#111;padding-top:80px;padding-bottom:80px\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"1200px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":2,\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#c9a96e\"}},\"fontFamily\":\"playfair-display\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-playfair-display-font-family\" style=\"color:#c9a96e\">What Our Clients Say</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"40px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"24px\",\"bottom\":\"24px\",\"left\":\"24px\",\"right\":\"24px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"8px\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"#1a1a1a\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-background\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;border-radius:8px;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e8d5a3\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e8d5a3\">\"The platform transformed our online presence. Page speed improved by 200% and our conversion rate doubled within weeks.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#999\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#999\"><strong style=\"color:#f5f5f5\">Sarah Mitchell</strong><br>CEO, Mitchell Enterprises</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"24px\",\"bottom\":\"24px\",\"left\":\"24px\",\"right\":\"24px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"8px\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"#1a1a1a\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-background\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;border-radius:8px;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e8d5a3\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e8d5a3\">\"Exceptional design quality and attention to detail. The GSAP animations give our site a premium feel that our competitors lack.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#999\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#999\"><strong style=\"color:#f5f5f5\">James Rodriguez</strong><br>Founder, Nova Studio</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"24px\",\"bottom\":\"24px\",\"left\":\"24px\",\"right\":\"24px\"}},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"8px\"}},\"backgroundColor\":\"#1a1a1a\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-background\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;border-radius:8px;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e8d5a3\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e8d5a3\">\"The mega menu and header builder alone saved us weeks of development. Truly the most complete WordPress theme available.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#999\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#999\"><strong style=\"color:#f5f5f5\">Emily Chen</strong><br>Marketing Director, Brightside Inc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->"
